author: imtheoneuneverknow
text:
Ahile ko bastabik kanun bamojim pani Rabi Jee doshi hunu hunna tyo katachhya satya kura ho. 
Yo video herdai garda maile Deepak jee le bhannu bhayeko kanun ko truti bhanera jun waha ko dharana ho tara mero dharana chahi yo kanun ma bhanda pani sidhai nyaya ra nyaya bamoji ko natija ko pachhyama ho ahile ko kanuni sandarbama. 
Yadhyapi, yehi prasanga lai joddai garda, manis ko kahina kahi suicidal thoughts habi bhayera suicide garna sakchha bhhane sandharba pani huna sakchha yo kura maile kina garna khojeko bhane ma yo world ko suicidal case high hune thau ma basdai ayeko tara highly social country bata yo thauma basobas gardai ayeko manchheko dharana ho. Arule jabarjasti garera atmahatya garne ra afai garne ma dherai antar chha. Afai garnelai, usko bigat jiban bata nai usle symptoms dekhayeko hunchha, tesaile tyo kurako lagi Nepal jasto desh ma kasari nunya(0 tolerance) tira lane bhanne kurako addhyan garnu dherai abasyak chha. 
Arko sandharma herda, yedi kasaile badhyatabas aru lai atmahatya garna bibas banayeko chha bhane yesto praman lai manyata dinu parchha ki jun sab manisle herda yo bibasta purna ho ra sajaya ko bhagidar hunu parchha bhanne tathya prasta hunchha. Mero bicharma chahi testo bibastapurna garayeko atmahatya ma chahi, written ra audio matra nabhai written ra video pani court ma dayar garnu parchha bhaane dharana ho. Yo court ma prastut gariyeko chha bhane yo case lai arko shreni ma rakhera yo manis sachainai atmahatya garna khojeko ho tara kasai lai thaha nadi ya pahilenai yo lachhyan dekayeko ya manashik rog bhayeko manchhe ho bhanne kanunin hisab ra tau tarika bata manyata deosh!
